                        <p>Each template uses Bootstrap to easily and efficiently scale your websites and applications with a single code base, from phones to tablets to desktops with CSS media queries.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-4">
                        <img alt="Components" src="Images/components.png" class="img-responsive">
