                    <p>Get all the dependency packages with <strong>npm install</strong> then build.</p>
                    <p>To build all the 3rd party packages and put them in the lib directory run <strong>gulp install</strong>.</p>
                    <p>Then to continuously build the less/style.less to the css directory and start a livereload web server on http://localhost run <strong>gulp</strong>.</p>
                </div>
